graph TD
    User((User/Student)) -->|Select Student/Theme| Frontend[React Web App]
    Admin((Administrator)) -->|Authenticate| Frontend
    Admin -->|Run Diagnostics| Frontend
    Admin -->|View Audit Logs| Frontend

    subgraph FrontendApp [Academic Performance Dashboard]
        UI[Tailwind UI Components]
        Logic[React State & Hooks]
        Data[Static JSON Student Data]
        Audit[In-Memory Audit Logger]
        Test[Self-Test Diagnostics]
    end

    UI --- Logic
    Logic --- Data
    Logic --- Audit
    Logic --- Test
